Package org.bluej.UMLextension

Class Preferences

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bluej.UMLextension.Preferences
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    bluej.extensions2.PreferenceGenerator
    class Preferences
extends Object
implements bluej.extensions2.PreferenceGenerator
    Long time ago Ian Utting developed UMLExtension for BlueJ https://www.bluej.org/extensions/UMLextension/UMLextension.jar https://www.bluej.org/extensions/extensions.html I (Milton Jesus Vera Contreras) decompiled JAR file and upgraded UML Extension to BlueJ5 using JavaFX. I add drag funtionality and change click event for double click event to close window. This class has several changes. All swing code was changed to JavaFX
